# Review UI

## Objective
Enable a secondary user to approve tasks sitting in the "Review" Kanban column.

## Tasks
1. Update the Kanban UI to highlight tasks in the "Review" column.
2. Add an "Approve" interaction on quests in Review (e.g., a button or a specific modal).
3. If the logged-in user is the assignee of the task in Review, disable or hide the Approve interaction.
4. Hook the approval UI into the `ApprovalLogic` backend mutation.
